---
import AdminLayout from '../../layouts/AdminLayout.astro';

const currentDate = new Date().toLocaleDateString();
---

<AdminLayout title="Implementation Plan">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Implementation Plan</h1>
  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">As of {currentDate}</p>

  <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Project Requirements</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        A comprehensive review of the project requirements, existing codebase, system architecture, and known issues.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Existing Codebase Review</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        An in-depth analysis of the existing codebase, including documentation and dependencies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">System Architecture</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        A detailed review of the system architecture and its dependencies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Known Issues and Technical Debt</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        Identification and documentation of known issues and technical debt.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Prioritized Action Plan</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        A prioritized action plan with specific tasks, estimated effort, dependencies, and success criteria.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Execution of the Implementation Plan</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        Documentation of the execution of the implementation plan, including addressing critical issues, following best practices, writing automated tests, and documenting changes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Validation</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        Documentation of the results of running test suites, code reviews, performance metrics, and success criteria.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Implementation Plan Steps</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Step 1: Comprehensive Review</li>
        <li>Step 2: Identify and Document</li>
        <li>Step 3: Prioritized Action Plan</li>
        <li>Step 4: Execute the Plan</li>
        <li>Step 5: Validate Work</li>
        <li>Step 6: Document Blockers and Decisions</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Critical Functionality Gaps</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Integration with external music databases</li>
        <li>Implementation of recurring schedules for Show Scheduling</li>
        <li>Comprehensive analytics in Admin Dashboard</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">High-Priority Bugs</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Intermittent authentication failures</li>
        <li>Performance issues with large playlists</li>
        <li>UI inconsistencies in the music library management</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Technical Improvements</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Refactor codebase to improve maintainability</li>
        <li>Optimize database queries for better performance</li>
        <li>Enhance security measures for user authentication</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</AdminLayout>
